title: Median age of first alcohol use among U.S. youth 1991 to 2015
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Average age in years. In total the number of data points it has is 23.
Overall Average age in years has increased over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 1991–1993 and 1992–1994.
The highest Average age in years, of value 14.64 was reached at Year 2013–2015
The lowest Average age in years, of value 13.65 was reported at Year 1991–1993
